      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name="xiajiadian"></a>
        Xiajiadian Culture
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=25656' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Xiàjiādiàn Wénhuà', 'Xiajiadian Culture')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>夏家店文化</a>
      </h3>
      <p>
        The pottery utensils below, from the Lower <span class='bookTitle'>Xiajiadian Culture</span> <a href='/word_detail.php?id=25515' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Xiàjiādiàn', 'Xiajiadian')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">夏家店</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=811' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '層 céng', 'measure word for layers, levels in a building, etc')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">层</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1412' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wénhuà', 'culture')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">文化</a> in Inner Mongolia was produced at the same time as the Bronze Age in parts of China 
        and show definite similarity with geometric patterns in Xia and Shang Dynasty bronze ware.
      </p>
