          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=25515' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Xiàjiādiàn', 'Xiajiadian')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">夏家店</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=811' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '層 céng', 'measure word for layers, levels in a building, etc')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">层</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1412' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wénhuà', 'culture')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">文化</a>（<a href='/word_detail.php?id=910' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '約 yuē', 'approximately')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">约</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=22414' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Gōng​yuán​ Qián', 'Before the Common Era (BCE)')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">公元前</a>2000〜<a href='/word_detail.php?id=681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qián', 'in front of / before')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">前</a>1500<a href='/word_detail.php?id=438' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nián', 'year')" 
